Suggestions:
Cumm Sales = 
        CALCULATE(  
                    SUM(Sales[Sales Amount]),
                    filter(
                            allselected('Date'),
                            'Date'[date] <=max('Date'[date])
                          )
                 )

Actual applied:
Latest Day Sum = 
        calculate (
                    sum (vw_revenue_metrics[DailyReimbursement]),
                    vw_revenue_metrics[CensusDate] = max(vw_revenue_metrics[CensusDate])
                  )
